# Orphaned SPM workspace data: this Xcode workspace has zero
# XCRemoteSwiftPackageReference entries; Tauri builds Swift packages via
# swift-rs (under target/) instead. Without this rule, Xcode would silently
# recreate Package.resolved with stale firebase-ios-sdk pins on every open,
# masking the real swift-rs version state (see tauri-plugin-frak-crashlytics
# README "Symbol upload" section).
